body:
The look on my face when more illegal and detrimental lockdowns are announced. üòÜ

For those that have come to the realisation that all of these lockdowns are not about covid19 with a survival rate of over 99%. 

The lockdowns, the mask wearing, the ‚Äòsocial‚Äô distancing are not legally binding upon anybody. They are ‚Äòmeasures‚Äô, ‚Äòguidelines‚Äô and ‚Äòrules‚Äô not laws. 

The lockdowns are killing more people than corona has, we know this now. So why more lockdowns? I suppose everybody has to research deeply and find these answers for themselves. 

But for those that feel bullied into these measures and feel they are wrong. You are within your legal rights to walk anywhere you like without a mask (the lockdown was presented because masks didn‚Äôt work, there have been no studies done of mask effectiveness. Yet now several months later; they are mandatory? They magically now work?). 

If a shop attendant asks you why you are not wearing a mask, it is sufficient for you to say you are exempt. If they ask you for proof, then they are breaking the law. Under the Disabilities Act of 2010 it is illegal to ask a person with a hidden disability what their disability is. Many people have been suing supermarkets/shops for this, they are rewarded between ¬£900-¬£9000 in compensation for emotional injury. 

Lockdowns are being used against the people now. They are also illegal. All our rights afforded to us under Common Law from the Magna Carta 1215 mean that any free person is exempt from any of this. 

Know your rights guys and go about your lawful business as usual. Stay strong and keep the joy in your lives. Keep breathing freely and smiling and remember none of our ancestors died for our freedoms so that we would hand them over to corrupt leaders with no resistance whatsoever.

Stand proud guys we are all free people. üíì ‚öñÔ∏èüíì
